{"tid":2364214,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–六個月前的BB不應打冷震","createTime":"2021-01-12T21:36:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-17T23:08:16.000Z","uid":38861,"like":77,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":22,"replies":[{"pid":"2049f6e5dcfdf8b60b6c3f692b4df02ada1ce992","tid":2364214,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T21:36:52.000Z","msg":"某部份類型的癌細胞非常嗜糖，因此吸收糖分的速度亦非常之快。<br />\n 18F-FDG PET/CT scan就是一種探測器官吸取糖分的技術，藉此推斷癌症發生的可能性。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5RbyR7f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5RbyR7f.jpg&h=b32ed088&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有一些癌細胞並不嗜糖，反而是喜愛脂肪酸等等，<br />\n但亦可以透過PET/CT scan這種技術對症下藥探測。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（圖2）圖中黑色圓點為糖分聚集並作新陳代謝的地方，<br />\n位置是鎖骨對上的位置。<br />\n到底係唔係癌症呢?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cv5ouT2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcv5ouT2.png&h=751e9c21&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n（圖3）黑色圓點地方並無異常淋巴的跡象，而且是位於脂肪部位。<br />\n黑色區域大有可能為啡色脂肪!<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/UJm7b7q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUJm7b7q.png&h=444d359a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n啡色脂肪延伸閱讀:<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/article/473954\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Farticle%2F473954&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=2840ee45\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/article/473954</a><br />\n<br />\n（圖4）嬰兒時候(1-6個月歲數)，調節體溫的系統尚未發展成熟，<br />\n他們並不懂得利用打冷震(肌肉顫抖)來保持體溫。<br />\n他們唯一的依靠就是啡色脂肪，啡色脂肪善於將糖分等營養轉化成熱力，為身體帶來溫暖。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZCRSoec.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZCRSoec.jpg&h=f9a51b43&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n隨歲數增長，調節體溫的系統漸趨發展成熟。啡色脂肪亦逐漸被白色脂肪取替，白色脂肪善於將吸收的營養作儲存之用，而非運用轉化成為熱力。<br />\n<br />\n而成人碩果僅存的啡色脂肪就在於鎖骨及.......<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n下回再續。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=30dd959c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=74d9d4e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n基於WhatsApp/Facebook等問題，IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n<br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12571205/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F12571205%2F&d=Eu1QSTPz0OFPBNy7%2BevvEXGrSSjb4k8A9Srgfm1924U%3D&h=d41f0805\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/12571205/</a>"},{"pid":"34bac87f936780d6b40e3e24469735d413078671","tid":2364214,"uid":199689,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T21:39:25.000Z","msg":"點解唔係深入淺出<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f739bde2a523a781f46d03741c50a144514833b7","tid":2364214,"uid":34119,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-12T21:43:08.000Z","msg":"條車呔